      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> finely</p>",
