    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid, with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>and<strong> onion wedges </strong>to the dish with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>sliced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p>",
