      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>dried thyme</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p>",
