      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[480ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong>,<strong> </strong>your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and<strong> bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, put the dish in the oven for 20 min, uncovered, or until the pepper is tender – this is your <strong>curry</strong></p>",
